<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="18Jun1925"><font color="red">18 June 1925</font> <i>BLHW</i> (to Harriet Weaver): I have been working all day through piles of notes and I hope the other man brings my sailcloth awning as the sun roasts the nape of my reflective head </div>
